From: Zou Dengming <marsow.zou@rock-chips.com>
Date: Mon, 15 May 2023 22:06:58 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] disable wbs and config pcm to slave mode default

1. disable wbs for rtk prefer it, and rk kernel not perfect ready
   for 16k.
2. change ESCO_DATA_PATH_PCM to 6 for pcm slave mode.

Change-Id: I8b457fe496c535d8a1076bc37150b8db93a0ef61
---
 rtkbt/bluetooth/bdroid_buildcfg.h | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/rtkbt/bluetooth/bdroid_buildcfg.h b/rtkbt/bluetooth/bdroid_buildcfg.h
index 4a527ef..8a78836 100644
--- a/rtkbt/bluetooth/bdroid_buildcfg.h
+++ b/rtkbt/bluetooth/bdroid_buildcfg.h
@@ -68,4 +68,9 @@
 #define BT_HCI_DEVICE_NODE_MAX_LEN 512
 
 #define KERNEL_MISSING_CLOCK_BOOTTIME_ALARM TRUE
+
+/*rockchip add start*/
+/*disable 16K/MSBC because rtk prefer cvsd*/
+#define DISABLE_WBS TRUE
+#define ESCO_DATA_PATH_PCM 6
 #endif
